54
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:32,160
without slowing down.

55
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,510
It was too late to slow down.

56
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,280
Is your car insured?

57
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:36,510
If you have insurance,

58
00:04:36,510 --> 00:04:37,160
