59
00:04:37,350 --> 00:04:38,070
Why should I?

60
00:04:38,070 --> 00:04:39,560
It's your responsibility.
Why should I apply for insurance?

61
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:42,440
Wait, why is it my responsibility?

62
