156
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:20,750
Hello.

157
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:23,190
Hello.

158
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:24,240
I have to go.

159
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,750
I am busy working. Bye.

160
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:28,870
Boyfriend again.

161
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,240
