234
00:15:06,990 --> 00:15:07,360
Cheers.

235
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:13,480
Nice wine.

236
00:15:13,990 --> 00:15:14,840
Want more?

237
00:15:22,110 --> 00:15:22,630
Cheers.

238
00:16:34,070 --> 00:16:34,840
Ms. Xia.

239
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,040
Good morning.

240
00:16:37,630 --> 00:16:38,360
