244
00:16:49,310 --> 00:16:51,430
Turn left after going out of the village.

245
00:16:51,430 --> 00:16:52,990
Go straight ahead.

246
00:16:52,990 --> 00:16:53,920
Just walk down the hill

247
00:16:53,920 --> 00:16:54,630
