248
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:55,670
Yes.

249
00:16:56,240 --> 00:16:57,070
Thank you, sir.

250
00:16:57,070 --> 00:16:57,990
Thank you for your care.
You are welcome.

251
00:16:57,990 --> 00:16:58,600
I am leaving.

252
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:01,400
