284
00:19:57,150 --> 00:19:57,840
Over there.

285
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:06,600
Come on.

286
00:20:15,840 --> 00:20:16,550
Laugh again.

287
00:20:19,190 --> 00:20:20,480
Come on.

288
00:20:21,550 --> 00:20:22,310
Forget it.

289
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:24,240
You go up first.

290
